# DFIR Platform API URL
# Set this to connect the portfolio to the DFIR-PLATFORM backend
# Example: http://localhost:8000 or https://your-api.example.com
VITE_DFIR_API_URL=

# =============================================================================
# API-KEY-FREE MODE (Default)
# =============================================================================
# This toolkit works WITHOUT API keys using free public sources:
# - DNS Blacklists (dnsbl.ahbl.org, spamhaus.org, etc.)
# - Abuse.ch (ThreatFox, URLhaus, MalwareBazaar)
# - NIST National Vulnerability Database
# - CIRCL CVE Search API
# - CISA Feeds and Advisories
# - SANS Internet Storm Center
# - Multiple security news RSS feeds
#
# No VirusTotal, AbuseIPDB, Shodan, GreyNoise, OTX, or URLScan keys needed!
#
# =============================================================================
# FEATURES
# =============================================================================
# Without backend (VITE_DFIR_API_URL not set):
# ✓ IOC Check (client-side pattern analysis)
# ✓ Domain Scan (client-side scoring)
# ✓ Phishing Analyzer (keyword/syntax analysis)
# ✓ Privacy Check (browser fingerprinting)
# ✓ Wiki / Knowledge Base
# ✓ Threat Actors Database
#
# With backend (VITE_DFIR_API_URL set):
# ✓ All client-side features PLUS:
# ✓ Live threat intelligence feeds
# ✓ RSS feed aggregation
# ✓ DNS blacklist checking
# ✓ Real-time vulnerability feeds
# ✓ Security news aggregation
# =============================================================================
